@REM==============================================================================

@node "PreRelease" "Pre-Release Informations"

                            @{b}Pre-Release Informations
                           ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

FAME is a brand new MailBox program which is continually becoming increasingly popular
and FAMEous as we can see on the very positive reactions we receive
daily.

We already have many bug-reports and suggestions and we believe we will
get lots more from the very first release on.

We work hard on fixing all reported bugs and realize suggestions as best we
can, but it's impossible to do it all at the same time.

The same with the documents.

The documents are not complete at all... we have to enhance and enlarge
the documents to tie in with the FAME executables.

You have bought FAME in an early stage, and because of this not everything
written here is 100% correct but we will work on it.


@{u}@{b}Unknown described parts in FAMEHydra.guide@{uu}@{ub}

 - Usage of Hydra (Command and key description).

 - How FAMEHydra works.

@endnode

