@REM==============================================================================

@node "NotImplemented" "Not implemented yet"

                              @{b}Not implemented yet
                             ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

              Soory, but this option is currently not implemented!

    It was not possible to implement all we want to yet, but because of the
     fact that FAME ist so much known yet and everbody cries for it we have
                        decided to pre-release FAME now.

     If we would first implement all stuff we want to have in FAME we need
                           a complete year for this.

      If you have registered  FAME you *MUST* agree with this, else it wouldn't
                         be possible to release FAME now.

                 Everything will be implemented but it takes time.

    If there is any really very important thing which isn't implemented yet
          please send a note to the @{"Development Team" link "FAME.guide/AboutDevTeam"} and we will try to
                       implement it as soon as possible.

@endnode

